<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="148" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="19.[173,1382,1044,2221]" pageId="19" pageNumber="148">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[175,890,1757,1786]" pageId="19" pageNumber="148">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
One of the Guyana specimens of Reig’s Opossum was collected in a pitfall trap, suggesting a ground-based habit.
</paragraph>
